body_html:
Hello, I met a problem like yours. I have a model in docker and I try to train it. It works and everything is ok. But later on , I try t train it, a problem occurs:
ImportError: /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow_internal.so: undefined symbol: _ZTIN10tensorflow17CostGraphDef_NodeE
Failed to load the native TensorFlow runtime.
Could you please give some suggestion? Thank you in advance.

ImportError: /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow_internal.so: undefined symbol: _ZTIN10tensorflow17CostGraphDef_NodeE
Failed to load the native TensorFlow runtime.
Could you please give some suggestion? Thank you in advance.
